                {
                    "paragraphs":[
                        "Pursuant to EFTA section 919(a)(2)(A), proposed \u00a7 205.31(b)(1) stated that a remittance transfer provider must make specified pre-payment disclosures to a sender, as applicable. The disclosures are discussed below."
