                "EFTA section 919(d)(3) directs the Bureau to issue final rules regarding appropriate remittance transfer cancellation and refund policies for senders within 18 months of the date of enactment of the Dodd-Frank Act. Proposed \u00a7 205.34 set forth new cancellation and refund rights for senders of remittance transfers, and they are finalized in renumbered \u00a7 1005.34 with changes to the proposed rule, discussed below."
